<F P=102> EA2404163194 (Clandestine) Radio Muhabura in French to 
Rwanda 1030 GMT 24 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> EA2404163194 </F>
<F P=104>  (Clandestine) Radio Muhabura </F>
