  [Text] SAPA reports that a bomb exploded in Germiston on 
the East Rand short while ago killing seven people and injuring 
50. The bomb apparently exploded on the corner of Knox and 
Odendaal streets. No further information is available. 
  Meanwhile the police on the West Rand have confirmed that a 
bomb exploded at a taxi rank across from Randfontein station 
