Corporation] interview there was prima facie evidence that the 
suspects had been involved in the explosions. They would be 
brought before the courts soon. 
  It was difficult to say whether more Afrikaner 
Weerstandsbeweging [Resistance Movement -- AWB] Ystergarde [Iron 
Guard] members were involved, Gen van der Merwe said, but the 
suspects came from a "certain circle" in the AWB. 
